data.description: Spacious single-family home located in the exceptional Ocean Springs School District, with close access to boat ramps and neighborhood park. This 3-bedroom, 2-bath home sits on over a half-acre and is beautifully surrounded by pine trees and live oaks. The high ceiling in the living room enhances the open floorplan, and the brick, wood-burning fireplace gives the room a homey feel. The huge master bedroom boasts a deep walk-in closet and large bath tub. Dual-vanities in both bathrooms, and the split floor plan places the guest bathroom perfectly. The front porch is an ideal place for rocking chairs and a cold drink, while the long driveway has an additional concrete slab to add more parking access to the already included two-car garage. The massive backyard includes a beautiful storage shed and a playground set that includes a slide and swings. The sunroom looks out into the backyard and is the perfect space for a fitness or kids room. This home isn't going to last -- schedule your showing before it's gone!
